OL,7,FMark and Ros Dowey said their 'world
OL,8,Fhas been shattered' since losing their
OL,9,Fson to suicide in December 2023, as
OL,10,FDigital Producer Sam Leader reports
OL,12,FWhen Murray Dowey left his parents
OL,13,Fwatching television downstairs to go
OL,14,Fup to his bedroom he was a happy
OL,15,Fsixteen-year-old boy.
OL,17,FJust hours later, Murray had taken his
OL,18,Fown life, having become the latest
OL,19,Fvictim of a surge of sextortion cases
